<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Pediatría en Casa — Acompañamiento pediátrico 24/7</title>
<meta name="description" content="Educación, triaje inteligente y consulta con el Dr. Enrique. Pediatría en Casa: acompañamiento médico para tu familia, las 24 horas." />
<style>
  /* ---------- Reset & base ---------- */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: #2b2b2b;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  :root {
    --azul-oscuro: #3a4f63;
    --azul-claro: #b8d4eb;
    --coral: #ff7b63;
    --coral-hover: #ff6048;
    --blanco: #ffffff;
    --gris: #f5f7fa;
    --texto: #2b2b2b;
    --shadow-sm: 0 4px 12px rgba(58,79,99,0.08);
    --shadow-md: 0 10px 30px rgba(58,79,99,0.15);
    --shadow-lg: 0 20px 50px rgba(58,79,99,0.25);
  }

  /* ---------- Navbar ---------- */
  .navbar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(14px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(14px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(58,79,99,0.08);
    transition: padding .25s ease, background .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
  }
  .navbar.scrolled {
    padding: 10px 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(58,79,99,0.08);
  }
  .nav-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--azul-oscuro);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45,106,95,0.25);
  }
  .nav-brand-text {
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--azul-oscuro);
  }
  .nav-brand-text small {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #6b7a8c;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 28px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--azul-oscuro);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: color .2s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--coral); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--coral);
    color: #fff !important;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, background .2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,123,99,0.3);
  }
  .nav-cta:hover {
    background: var(--coral-hover);
    color: #fff !important;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(255,123,99,0.45);
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .navbar { padding: 10px 18px; }
    .nav-links { gap: 14px; }
    .nav-links li:not(:last-child) { display: none; }
    .nav-brand-text small { display: none; }
  }

  /* ---------- Sections ---------- */
  section {
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  #hero { padding-top: 110px; }

  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ---------- Typography ---------- */
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #4a5666; }

  /* ---------- Buttons ---------- */
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 16px 38px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease, background .25s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .btn-coral {
    background: var(--coral);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,123,99,0.35);
  }
  .btn-coral:hover {
    background: var(--coral-hover);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(255,123,99,0.5);
  }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--azul-oscuro);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  /* ---------- Section 1: Hero ---------- */
  #hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a4f63 0%, #2c3e50 60%, #1f2d3a 100%);
    color: #fff;
  }
  #hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(184,212,235,0.15) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,123,99,0.12) 0%, transparent 45%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-text h1 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .hero-text p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
    max-width: 520px;
  }
  .hero-emoji {
    font-size: 200px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3));
  }

  /* ---------- Section 2: Blog ---------- */
  #blog { background: #fff; }
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .blog-side-emoji {
    font-size: 180px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .blog-content h2 { color: var(--coral); }
  .blog-content > p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 36px 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border: 2px solid #eef2f7;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease, border-color .3s ease;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-color: var(--azul-claro);
  }
  .card-emoji {
    font-size: 56px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .card h3 { color: var(--azul-oscuro); }
  .card p { font-size: 0.97rem; color: #5b6878; }

  /* ---------- Section 3: Triaje ---------- */
  #triaje { background: var(--gris); }
  .triaje-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .triaje-text h2 { color: var(--azul-oscuro); }
  .triaje-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .triaje-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .triaje-features li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #4a5666;
  }
  .triaje-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    color: var(--coral);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  .chat-mockup {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    position: relative;
  }
  .chat-mockup::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 14px;
    left: 24px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ff5f57;
    box-shadow: 18px 0 0 #febc2e, 36px 0 0 #28c840;
  }
  .chat-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 18px 0 16px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eef2f7;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .chat-avatar {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b8d4eb, #3a4f63);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
  }
  .chat-header div strong { display: block; color: var(--azul-oscuro); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .chat-header div span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #6dbf73; }
  .chat-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .msg {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    max-width: 80%;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
    animation: msgIn .5s ease forwards;
  }
  .msg.bot {
    background: #eef4fb;
    color: var(--azul-oscuro);
    border-bottom-left-radius: 6px;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .msg.user {
    background: var(--coral);
    color: #fff;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 6px;
    align-self: flex-end;
  }
  .msg:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: .2s; }
  .msg:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .8s; }
  .msg:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .msg:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.2s; }
  @keyframes msgIn {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .triaje-emoji {
    font-size: 150px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  /* ---------- Section 4: Dr. Enrique ---------- */
  #dr-enrique { background: #fff; }
  .dr-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .dr-photo-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .dr-photo {
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b8d4eb, #3a4f63);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 6px solid #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 110px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .dr-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .dr-text h2 { color: var(--azul-oscuro); }
  .dr-text > p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  }
  .credentials {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .credential {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: var(--gris);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--coral);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .credential-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .credential strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--azul-oscuro);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }
  .credential span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #5b6878;
  }
  .dr-emoji {
    font-size: 140px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* ---------- Section 5: Propósito ---------- */
  #proposito {
    background: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  #proposito h2 { color: var(--azul-oscuro); }
  #proposito > .container > p {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .big-emoji {
    font-size: 180px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }
  .values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  .value {
    padding: 32px 20px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid #eef2f7;
    transition: transform .3s ease, border-color .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease;
  }
  .value:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: var(--coral);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .value-emoji {
    font-size: 52px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .value h3 { color: var(--azul-oscuro); font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .value p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #5b6878; }

  /* ---------- Section 6: CTA Final ---------- */
  #cta-final {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a4f63 0%, #2c3e50 60%, #1f2d3a 100%);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  #cta-final::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255,123,99,0.18) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(184,212,235,0.18) 0%, transparent 40%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  #cta-final .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  #cta-final h2 { color: #fff; }
  #cta-final > .container > p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .dancing-emoji {
    font-size: 180px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .testimonial {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .stars { color: #ffd166; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  /* ---------- Animations ---------- */
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes slideInLeft {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-40px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }
  @keyframes slideInRight {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(40px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }
  /* PediBot — organic breathing + gentle sway, NOT robotic */
  @keyframes pediBot {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0)    rotate(-3deg) scale(1);    }
    20%  { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(2deg)  scale(1.04); }
    40%  { transform: translateY(-3px) rotate(5deg)  scale(1.08); }
    60%  { transform: translateY(-9px) rotate(-1deg) scale(1.05); }
    80%  { transform: translateY(-4px) rotate(-5deg) scale(1.03); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0)    rotate(-3deg) scale(1);    }
  }
  /* Slightly livelier variant for the final-CTA emoji */
  @keyframes pediBotJoyful {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0)     rotate(-5deg) scale(1);    }
    25%  { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(4deg)  scale(1.06); }
    50%  { transform: translateY(-4px)  rotate(5deg)  scale(1.08); }
    75%  { transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(-4deg) scale(1.05); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0)     rotate(-5deg) scale(1);    }
  }

  .animate-fade  { animation: fadeIn 1s ease forwards; }
  .animate-left  { animation: slideInLeft 1s ease forwards; }
  .animate-right { animation: slideInRight 1s ease forwards; }

  /* All PediBot instances share the same organic, breathing motion */
  .hero-emoji,
  .blog-side-emoji,
  .triaje-emoji,
  .dr-emoji,
  .big-emoji {
    animation: pediBot 4.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform-origin: center bottom;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  .hero-emoji { animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease .3s both, pediBot 4.5s ease-in-out 1.5s infinite; }
  .dancing-emoji {
    animation: pediBotJoyful 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform-origin: center bottom;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero-emoji, .blog-side-emoji, .triaje-emoji,
    .dr-emoji, .big-emoji, .dancing-emoji {
      animation: none !important;
    }
  }

  /* Reveal-on-scroll */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity .9s ease, transform .9s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid, .blog-grid, .triaje-grid, .dr-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-text p, .triaje-text p, .blog-content > p { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .values { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .hero-emoji, .blog-side-emoji, .triaje-emoji, .dr-emoji { font-size: 140px; }
    .big-emoji, .dancing-emoji { font-size: 130px; }
    .triaje-features { display: inline-block; text-align: left; }
    .credential { text-align: left; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    section { padding: 60px 18px; }
    .values { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .btn { padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 1rem; }
    .dr-photo { width: 220px; height: 220px; font-size: 90px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============ NAVBAR ============ -->
<header class="navbar" id="navbar">
  <a class="nav-brand" href="#hero" aria-label="Pediatría en Casa — Inicio">
    <!-- Logo: SVG inline (reemplazable por <img src="logo.png" class="nav-logo" alt="Pediatría en Casa">) -->
    <svg class="nav-logo" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <rect width="100" height="100" rx="14" fill="#2d6a5f"/>
      <g fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M14 48 L50 16 L86 48"/>
        <path d="M22 46 L22 84"/>
        <path d="M78 46 L78 84"/>
      </g>
      <g fill="#fff">
        <circle cx="44" cy="40" r="6.5"/>
        <path d="M32 52 Q34 47 44 47 Q53 47 56 55 L56 68 Q52 76 44 76 Q34 76 32 68 Z"/>
        <circle cx="60" cy="52" r="5"/>
        <path d="M52 58 Q58 57 64 60 Q67 64 65 71 Q59 73 53 71 Z"/>
      </g>
    </svg>
    <span class="nav-brand-text">
      Pediatría en Casa
      <small>Acompañamiento 24/7</small>
    </span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#blog">Educación</a></li>
      <li><a href="#triaje">Triaje</a></li>
      <li><a href="#dr-enrique">Dr. Enrique</a></li>
      <li><a href="#proposito">Propósito</a></li>
      <li><a href="#cta-final" class="nav-cta">Crear cuenta</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- ============ SECCIÓN 1: HERO ============ -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h1 class="animate-left">¿Son las 2 de la mañana?</h1>
        <p class="animate-left" style="animation-delay:.2s">
          Tu hijo tiene fiebre y no sabes qué hacer. Estamos aquí: educación, triaje inteligente y el Dr. Enrique a un clic. <strong>24 horas, 7 días.</strong>
        </p>
        <a href="#blog" class="btn btn-coral animate-fade" style="animation-delay:.5s">Explorar ahora</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🤖</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ SECCIÓN 2: BLOG ============ -->
<section id="blog">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="blog-grid">
      <div class="blog-side-emoji reveal" aria-hidden="true">🤖</div>
      <div class="blog-content">
        <h2 class="reveal">Primero: Educación</h2>
        <p class="reveal">
          Información pediátrica clara, basada en evidencia y escrita en español. Aprende antes de que aparezcan las dudas.
        </p>
        <div class="cards">
          <article class="card reveal">
            <span class="card-emoji">🌡️</span>
            <h3>Fiebre</h3>
            <p>Cuándo preocuparse, qué hacer y cuándo consultar.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal">
            <span class="card-emoji">😴</span>
            <h3>Sueño</h3>
            <p>Rutinas, despertares y descanso saludable por edad.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal">
            <span class="card-emoji">👶</span>
            <h3>Desarrollo</h3>
            <p>Hitos, alimentación y crecimiento mes a mes.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

